{"tid":780334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"RV Irene公開了和BP Jennie的友好關係","createTime":"2018-08-15T05:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T15:56:27.000Z","uid":51412,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b745bf933b0820ae2d6fa3a89d98c4a8ddbb857b","tid":780334,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"14日在JTBC《Idol Room》中Red Velvet作為嘉賓出演當天Irene提及了有關BLACKPINKJennie在自己的相關搜索詞中出現的事情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dispatch.cdnser.be/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/20180814194847_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdispatch.cdnser.be%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F20180814194847_1.jpg&h=d24390e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIrene說:&ldquo;因為和BLACKPINK Jennie之前是同一間美容院所以才慢慢變親近&quot;Irene 接著說:<br />\n因為我比較認生是Jennie一看到我就叫歐逆主動與我親近，所以也漸漸開始變熟。<br />\n<br />\n被問到見面時會做什麼事時，Irene說：&ldquo;見面的話一定會一起吃飯&rdquo;但因為行程很忙碌，所以不能常常見面，不過偶爾會聯繫。接著說，我和粉絲們一起辦的生日會上，和Jennie有過視訊通話，因為和粉絲們在一起不方便聊，掛斷前Jennie表示自己也是REVELUV呢，看來BLACKPINK的Jennie也Red Velvet粉絲呢。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在當天的節目中，Red Velvet成員們展開的Havana舞對決吸引了人們的關注。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0pYGY0Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0pYGY0Q.gif&h=4eeaa409&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27a22e8bde2798821b8271c34320a180b15b992e","tid":780334,"uid":55519,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:08:51.000Z","msg":"同一間整容醫院"},{"pid":"265e7d803436b1d39761f0e4cda0a0bbca706392","tid":780334,"uid":165368,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"支持友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5694b256063a365516033f91d10f653433c358b","tid":780334,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d918d847ddb061d31998a4b66204a6d1c7e295e","tid":780334,"uid":115441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci